name: Quarantine Funk
description:
!! SOUND ON !!

This is from an Instagram Reels & Tik Tok video I did during the beginning of quarantine. I haven't seen any NFTs of this kind so i am hoping this encourages other creators to do the same :D

Instruments used:
- Salt and Pepper container used as a shaker
- Frying Pan used as a cowbell
- Epiphone Les Paul Studio
- Ibanez Bass
- Drums and other sounds on Ableton Live 11

Composed | Produced on Ableton Live 11
